Quest:All You Need To Do

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Hypothetically Speaking

Given By: Captain K'torr J'rrol

Giver Location: Tyrian Gorge
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Talk to Dorian BrightEyes
Hand In: Dorian BrightEyes

Reward:

75
7,750


Leads to:

Take Me In

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to All You Need To Do should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to All You Need To Do in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
